<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200905/69c5dad553a247659a0025c4befe2521.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>迎走了静姐真的啥都好说，下一轮公布轮到蓝盈莹和她的好姐妹黄龄，俩人互看手卡没问题。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200905/b1ae5ecebb274cd9843a0374c50444e6.png" max-width="600" /></p>
